<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<center style="width: 100%; table-layout: fixed; background-color: #f4f7f6; padding-bottom: 60px;">
<table class="main" style="margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; border-spacing: 0; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;" width="100%">
	
		<tr>
			<td style="padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.mainstreet.org/"><img alt="Main Street America Logo" src="https://nationalmainstreetcenter2.my.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015aJ00000EU9H7&amp;oid=00Dfm000000BWKj&amp;lastMod=1770631915000" style="max-width: 250px; border: 0;" width="250" /></a></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="content" style="padding: 30px 40px; text-align: left;">
			<h1 style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; color: #00466a; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;">Membership Expired!</h1>

			<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Hi {{{Recipient.Name}}},</p>

			<p>This is a notification that your membership&nbsp;{{{Recipient.Active_Membership_Type__c}}} with&nbsp;{{{Recipient.Account_Name__c}}} has expired as of today {{{Recipient.Active_Membership_End_Date__c}}}.</p>

			<p>To ensure you don't lose access to your exclusive benefits and services, please renew your membership as soon as possible.<br />
			<br />
			If you have already renewed your membership, please disregard this email.</p>

			<p>We thank you for your continued partnership.</p>
			&nbsp;

			<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
				
					<tr>
						<td align="center" style="padding: 10px 0;"><a class="cta-button" href="https://members.mainstreet.org/my-account" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #d9662d; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">Access Your Member Portal</a></td>
					</tr>
				
			</table>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="footer" style="background-color: #333333; color: #bbbbbb; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px;">
			<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Main Street America<br />
			53 W. Jackson Blvd., Suite 350, Chicago, IL 60604</p>

			<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"><a href="https://members.mainstreet.org/my-account/settings" style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;">Update Subscription Preferences</a> | <a href="[LINK_TO_CONTACT_US]" style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;">Contact Us</a></p>
			</td>
		</tr>
	
</table>
</center>
</body>
</html>